          "description": "Hiroshi Hasegawa is an animation planner and producer, and the founder/representative director of Studio Deen.\n\nHe worked as a finishing/clean-up inspector at [Sunrise](https://anilist.co/studio/14/) until he founded [Studio DEEN](https://anilist.co/studio/37) in 1975, which at that time was just a finishing studio. In 1982 Deen was made into an animation production studio.",
